These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: drama, fantasy, horror, adventure, crime, satire, mystery
 1. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching crime movies##5
 2. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere between the person watching satire movies and the person watching crime movies##7
 3. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere between the person watching satire movies and the person watching drama movies##7
 4. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5
 5. the person watching mystery movies is not to the left of the person watching satire movies##8
 6. the person watching fantasy movies is in an odd position##4
 7. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
 8. the person watching satire movies is somewhere between the person watching crime movies and the person watching mystery movies##7
 9. the person watching horror movies is not to the right of the person watching adventure movies##8
10. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |  5   |  6  |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | drama | fantasy | horror | adventure | satire | mystery |

