.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-2::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: rugby, soccer, biathlon, tennis, cycling, rowing, sailing
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who's sport is rowing##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##5
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5
 4. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
 6. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##5
 7. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 8. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 9. the person who's sport is sailing is in an even position##4
10. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |       5       |    6     |      7       |
| Sport   | tennis | soccer | rowing | sailing | biathlon | rugby | cycling |

