.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: hiking, collecting, rock-climbing, card-games, board-games, gardening, writing
 1. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##8
 2. the person who's hobby is writing is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
 4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
 5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
 6. the person who's hobby is writing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##8
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person who's hobby is collecting##7
 8. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is hiking is not to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##8
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |   5   |    6    |    7    |
| Hobby   | board-games | gardening | card-games | writing | hiking | rock-climbing | collecting |

