 2. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 3. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 5. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
 6. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the person drinking sprite##8
 7. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking 7up##7
 8. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
 9. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking cola##2
10. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
11. the person drinking water is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2    |       3       |    4     |      5      |  6   |    7     |
| Beverage   | water | tea | soy-milk | 7up | fanta | cola | sprite |

