 6. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 7. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the roller##5
 8. the person driving the van is in an odd position##4
 9. the person driving the taxi is not to the right of the person driving the roller##8
10. the person driving the car is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5
11. the person driving the car is not to the right of the person driving the helicopter##8
12. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
13. the person driving the van is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
14. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2      |     3      |  4  |    5    |   6   |    7    |
| Transport   | taxi | roller | bike | car | van | helicopter | motorbike |

